    "A detailed description of the measurements of the exhaust gas is covered in the Methods section.",
    "The data from the 9-channel sensor array measured for each target gas was assigned to one class, forming a total of 6 classes equal to the number of target gases.",
    "As a result of the measurement, the differences in the eigengraph waveforms for each gas type were clear enough to be distinguished through the characteristic points of each waveform with the naked eye (Fig. 5, Supplementary Fig.",
    "In particular, in the case of gasoline and diesel engine exhausts, very unpredictable and unique waveforms were observed due to the mixture of various reactions from individual components.",
    "This result support with our argument about the existence of eigengraph."
